Angle:
 Adjust the angle of your turret according to the new enemy Postion.
Use '+','-' button to increment or decrement angle respectively,or click on angle button and control the angle with mouse

Power:
Adjust the Power level according to your Angle And distance between your enemy the Power level decides the launch velocity of Projectile
Use '+','-' button to increment or decrement Power level  respectively.

Weapons:
Choose from set of weapons that yoy chose.
Different weapons deal with Different damage and have different damage radius

Fire:
Use the fire Weapon to launch your Projectile.
